{"tid":2411428,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"華留學生無做新冠核酸檢測　遭美國大學開除處罰","createTime":"2021-02-17T10:20:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-17T10:46:47.000Z","uid":271829,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ed882975a25b776c79f417ad894e7556ba002aed","tid":2411428,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T10:20:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20210217/photo/bkn-20210217173703667-0217_00952_001_01p.jpg?20210217173820\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20210217%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20210217173703667-0217_00952_001_01p.jpg%3F20210217173820&h=5d230ea8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網上的聯署請願，圖為涉事博士生。<br />\n<br />\n內媒周二（16日）報道，一名在美國留學的中國籍陳姓博士生，疑因不知校方更改新冠肺炎規定的情況下，去年秋季學期未有按照要求進行核酸檢測。校方隨後追究責任，陳某向研究生僱員組織（GEO）求助，惟雙方出席與校方的聽證會上疑遭一錘定音，直接被開除一年學籍。目前，上訴兩次不果的陳某及其母親或會面臨遣返回國。<br />\n<br />\n涉事留學生陳毅東（Yidong Chen，音譯）在美國伊利諾伊州大學厄巴納-香佩恩分校（UIUC）就讀，他在上個春季學期因照顧母親及躲避疫情，留在家中上課及完成研究工作，符合校方規定的「100%遙距工作則毋須進行檢測」要求。惟至去年12月21日，他卻遭通知自己違反規定，即沒有在秋季學期開始時參與校方的集體檢測。<br />\n<br />\n陳男事後向GEO求助，後者除了在官網發出請願信外，亦在請願網站召集聯署。報道指，校方在聽證會上只問及與事件無關的提問，GEO代表亦不得發言，陳自辯的時間及機會不多，整場聽證會不足10分鐘便結束，而校方得出的結果是開除陳男的一年學籍，且即時生效，需撰寫兩篇1,000字檢討書、在大學警方監督執行下不得踏入校園，以及做80小時社區服務等處罰。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20210217/photo/bkn-20210217173703667-0217_00952_001_02b.jpg?20210217173820\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20210217%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20210217173703667-0217_00952_001_02b.jpg%3F20210217173820&h=e9d9f225&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n組織在本周持續更新狀況。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20210217/photo/bkn-20210217173703667-0217_00952_001_03b.jpg?20210217173820\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20210217%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20210217173703667-0217_00952_001_03b.jpg%3F20210217173820&h=68fc9702&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n組織在其官網張貼了請願信。"},{"pid":"419812bea44c08d46fb6f71c4d216d6e28ed7423","tid":2411428,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T10:21:39.000Z","msg":"又辱華"},{"pid":"82b73f018c63d8adc98701dd6a95485a2d42feb7","tid":2411428,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T10:22:50.000Z","msg":"開除定停學？   <br />\n開除學籍一年？"},{"pid":"262b050b8392f3d519924c6a66ca0902f3cf3bc1","tid":2411428,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T10:26:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.wcia.com/news/local-news/student-says-he-was-dismissed-from-uiuc-over-covid-19-testing-non-compliance/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wcia.com%2Fnews%2Flocal-news%2Fstudent-says-he-was-dismissed-from-uiuc-over-covid-19-testing-non-compliance%2F&d=bV20Ktv%2Bt3m81RcJrVEN2xhXM9JohKQ1t0lxADMilzY%3D&h=dadae40a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.wcia.com/news/local-news/student-says-he-was-dismissed-from-uiuc-over-covid-19-testing-non-compliance/</a>"},{"pid":"7ec55338e1f3c9a9f5dbde00adb53998db231b6b","tid":2411428,"uid":105924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82b73f018c63d8adc98701dd6a95485a2d42feb7","tid":2411428,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T10:22:50.000Z","msg":"開除定停學？   <br />\n開除學籍一年？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T10:46:47.000Z","msg":"應該係停學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}